          but doesn't work on your friends laptop</span
        >
      </p>

      <p class="mt-4 text-base text-gray-500">
        Reach out on our unofficial support platform.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 mt-12 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-12">
        <div>
          <p class="text-base font-medium text-accent-900">
            Semplice Community
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
            Create a discussion and get help from like-minded developers.
          </p>
          <div class="flex mt-4">
            <a
              href="#"
              class="flex items-center justify-center h-10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold transition-all bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-lg text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-500"
