          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
            Create a discussion and get help from like-minded developers.
          </p>

          <div class="flex mt-4">
            <a
              href="#"
              class="flex items-center justify-center h-10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold transition-all bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-lg text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-500"
              >Create a case
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div>
          <div>
            <span class="text-xl font-medium leading-tight text-accent-900"
              >Submit a case to our Customer Success Team.
            </span>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Which account is affected?</p>
